{
  "text": "A. Demographic Profile of Respondents A total of 465 respondents participated in the data collection, but only 453 responses were valid and included in the next data processing. The majority of the participants were male (71.7%). This gender profile confirmed prior studies that reported the majority of multiplayer video games were male [CITATION_1] , [CITATION_2] . More than half of the participants Puspitasari, Syahputra, Raharjana, & Jie Journal of Information Systems Engineering and Business Intelligence, 2018, 4(2), 131-138 134 played MVG few times a day (60.9%) with the last playing time was less than one month (83.4%). Table I presents the demographic profile of the respondents.",
